Louise Latimer (actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Louise_Latimer_(actress) 0 Louise Latimer (March 6, 1913 – June 16, 1973) was an American film actress. She starred opposite John Wayne in the 1937 California Straight Ahead!. Born in Brooklyn, New York, she graduated from Erasmus Hall High School. During the Second World War she was active with the American Red Cross and various Catholic charities, helping to promote the war effort.
